{"tid":1467603,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"成班都九唔搭八，你慢慢陪佢地捉鬼喇，連藍屍都不如","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:25:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:32:56.000Z","uid":196538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"85132316e8fc344fa030d45931889eed6afc50a1","tid":1467603,"uid":196538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:25:16.000Z","msg":"藍屍無腦，同狗無乜關係，活係自已世，但係就憑佢盲撐犬呢一點，已經贏哂我地<br />\n<br />\n相反我地呢？手足前手足後，又話做乜撚都唔割？依家呢？點解出面咁多post都割黎割去？係因為9成9係三毛阿<br />\n<br />\n記住，捉鬼唔係重點，但必須要有。我地要俾警告營造白色恐怖俾返d犬，做鬼無好下場，唔好俾佢地放鬼放得咁輕鬆，以為扮暈就可以叫救護無事，但係係捉鬼呢方面我都未諗到最好既方法<br />\n<br />\n再加上我地呢2個月進化得太快，所以一定會犯錯，so what?有乜好割？犬見到就最開心<br />\n<br />\n記住我地唔係藍屍阿，有腦架，識分事非黑白，唔好因爲大量三毛入侵就俾佢地轉風向<br />\n<br />\n一句講晒，就算手足柒左都唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋我唔認為今日手足係機場做既野係柒，ok?<br />\n<br />\n係手足既就會明，如果每次有唔岩你心水既行動你就割既話，對唔住，我唔係你手足<br />\n<br />\n記住，手足係點都唔會割<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對唔住，頭先語氣重左少少，唔好意思<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Q-T-0nIUzsc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQ-T-0nIUzsc&d=4IYAvm%2F2ThyFbSIl4Y3Ij73SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=afcf7649\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Q-T-0nIUzsc</a>"},{"pid":"6ee54855a94d3be47fdc6970c379c3a9a51aad95","tid":1467603,"uid":196538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:25:34.000Z","msg":"自推十下"},{"pid":"e256f279803d29e75a87ef97e7260207c55de208","tid":1467603,"uid":203619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:25:42.000Z","msg":"我只推 正常POST<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/RfNfTgW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRfNfTgW.png&h=52691539&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日我留意到最大單係警察係機場用槍指嚇市民<br />\n你地又留意到咩呢?<br />\n希望大家理性啲 幫手推返正常POST<br />\n<br />\n一句講哂<br />\n鬼係捉唔哂，大局為重"},{"pid":"2dffb082ae3b631da8c50af572d81c8a2ab46169","tid":1467603,"uid":196538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:25:59.000Z","msg":"自推十下"},{"pid":"4381d4bb22e4af2c1a10a707ebddfd1a41fcd7a2","tid":1467603,"uid":196538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:26:39.000Z","msg":"自推十下"},{"pid":"24e75f98b1d456f37ea352fa88aee0a1a0d9348e","tid":1467603,"uid":196538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:27:14.000Z","msg":"自推十下"},{"pid":"42bcd69bdc4c380cf85eb7b2fddbcf3705880c27","tid":1467603,"uid":196538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:28:10.000Z","msg":"自推十下"},{"pid":"a063e5f17d11093b20b93e0440072cca0df0af74","tid":1467603,"uid":61840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:32:56.000Z","msg":"各位手足今日可能做得唔完美，但係可接受，同埋仍然雖然改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不割既意思就係唔好指責，可以提出意見，可以唔理解，可以唔接受，但唔可以將手足分成一批又一批唔同既人，我地要記住我地係兄弟爬山，唔單只要各自努力，更加要互相扶持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}